backend/test_audit/
# Ignore local .claude state (settings.local.json, backups, caches) but TRACK the
# enforcement agent definitions so the four-agent gate is identical on every
# machine/CI. A wholesale-ignored dir can't re-include a child, so the parent must
# be `.claude/*` (not `.claude/`) for the `!` negation to take effect.
.claude/*
!.claude/agents/
.venv/
*_output.txt
query-*.json
run_*.py
